name: Wallykazam!
overview: The adventures of a boy named Wally Trollman and his pet dragon, Norville.

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: Wally and norville is going to an adventure on The 3rd Season

episodes.name: Naptime for Borgelorp
episodes.overview: Wally agrees to babysit Ogre Doug's rambunctious pet Borgelorp, and make sure it takes a nap. But when Bobgoblin feeds the Borgelorp purple flowers, the creature starts to behave in surprising ways.

episodes.name: Castle Caper
episodes.overview: Wally uses a magic word to build Norville's castle, then Bobgoblin invades the castle.

episodes.name: The Rock Can Talk
episodes.overview: Rockelle, a rock that Wally brings to life by his magic leads them to a treasure hunt to the Top of the Peak so they can find "The 3 Times Really Big Treasure".

episodes.name: How To Bathe Your Dragon
episodes.overview: Wally encourages Norville to take a bath during party time, but Bobgoblin steals the Letter "B" just because It starts with his name.

episodes.name: Dragon Hiccups
episodes.overview: Wally needs to find all the ingredients so he can mix up a magic potion to stop Norville's hiccups.

episodes.name: Picnic: Impossible
episodes.overview: When a storm ruins Gina's Picnic, Wally and his friends prepare a giant surprise picnic inside Gina Giant's house for her.

episodes.name: Totally Swamped
episodes.overview: When Wally's Glider lands in Stan's Swamp, Stan challenges Wally orders to get his glider back after he'll make Stan laugh. It is not an easy task at all, because he never laughed, smiled, and even giggled.

episodes.name: Day In The Dark
episodes.overview: When Norville loses his favorite toy, "Squeaky Cyclops", Wally, Norville, Ogre Doug and Libby Light Sprite set out to retrieve Norville's toy that has been taken by a female Night Dragon, as Norville to face his fears of the dark.

episodes.name: The Great Wishing Potato
episodes.overview: When Libby Light Sprite loses her voice, Bobgoblin suggests that the only way to bring her voice back, is by wishing her voice by "The Great Wishing Potato".

episodes.name: Running Rita
episodes.overview: When a magic word, "Run", makes Gina Giant's doll, Running Rita run away, she and Wally sets off to save her while Norville looks after Gina's Dolls.

episodes.name: The Cake Monster
episodes.overview: When a Cake Monster steals Ogre Doug's delicious cake, Wally and Norville set out to retrieve it. Then they discover that the Cake Monster's Birthday is the Same day on Ogre Doug's Birthday.

episodes.name: Great Galloping Goblins
episodes.overview: When Bobgoblin becomes a bandit and rides on the house like a horse, Wally, Norville, Libby Light Sprite and Ogre Doug set out to stop him from riding a house.

episodes.name: Victor the Villain
episodes.overview: While they were playing superheroes, Wally uses a magic word to Conjure a Villain so they can have a Super Villain to play with in superheroes.

episodes.name: Snow Place Like Home
episodes.overview: When Norville discovers a Baby Dragon (who is later a snow dragon) near their house, Wally and Norville set out to The Top of Mount Chilomanjaro to bring him back to his mother.

episodes.name: The Switching Stone
episodes.overview: When Norville discovers a stone that can glow, Wally and Gina change sizes when they touch a stone. Then Bobgoblin dubs himself "Biggoblin" after he switches sizes with Wally.

episodes.name: Play It Again, Stan
episodes.overview: Wally and his Friends teach Stan of the Swamp how to play before his niece Marsha of the Marsh visits.

episodes.name: A Tiny Problem
episodes.overview: When Libby Light Sprite discovers a "Flower that will Shrink You", Wally and Norville accidentally shrunk themselves. Then Wally and Norville encounter a Whittle named "Wendy" who can lead them on a Quest to find "the Berry that makes you big again".

episodes.name: Castle Cafe
episodes.overview: Wally and his friends transforms a pretend cafe into a real cafe when he ranged the bell saying, "lunch is ready at Wally's Castle Cafe!" and his friends come over.

episodes.name: The Dragon Games
episodes.overview: Norville, who is Determined to win, competes in the Dragon Games but Bobgoblin pretends to be a dragon to win a contest.

episodes.name: Mustache Day
episodes.overview: When Wally, Norville and Libby Light Sprite discover a Tremendous Treat at Wizard Jeff's House, Jeff challenges Wally and his Friends to get the Tremendous Treat before it turns into Underpants.

episodes.name: Wally Saves the Trollidays
episodes.overview: When Wally and Norville encounter an Elf name Elfelfa who's having trouble delivering a sack of wishes to the Jingle Troll, Wally and Norville Decide to Help her deliver the sack of wishes to the Jingle Troll before the Trollidays begin.

episodes.name: The Big Goblin Problem, part 1
episodes.overview: Wally's uncle Steve the Skydasher arrives with his dragon Victoria who Norville likes. As Steve and Victoria leave to rescue George the Elf, Bobgoblin gets ahold of doubling bubbles and has himself a clone dance party.

episodes.name: The Big Goblin Problem, part 2
episodes.overview: Wally's uncle Steve the Skydasher arrives with his dragon Victoria who Norville likes. As Steve and Victoria leave to rescue George the Elf, Bobgoblin gets ahold of doubling bubbles and has himself a clone dance party.

episodes.name: Hopgoblin
episodes.overview: Hattier turns Bobgoblin into a bunny and is Bunnygoblin and flies away on Hattie the Witch's broomstick without asking.

episodes.name: The Explorers Club
episodes.overview: Wally and Ogre Doug formed a club for explorers to find a rare chickenphant. Then, Hattie the Witch started a rival club with Bobgoblin.

episodes.name: Mission for Mom
episodes.overview: Wally goes to get his mom Mrs. Trollman her favorite flower for Mother's Day, with the Help from Libby Light Sprite.

episodes.name: The Nice Ninjas
episodes.overview: Wally lets Norville decide what words starting with 'n' to make, and Norville wants to play ninjas. Their ninja skills get put to the test when they conjure a naughty noodle, who teams with Bobgoblin to serve up mischief.

episodes.name: Home Swamp Home
episodes.overview: Wally, Libby Light Sprite and Stan search for a humbug that makes the humming of a Humbug make the Honkweeds go away and never ever come back.

episodes.name: The Goblin Cold
episodes.overview: Bobgoblin has come down with a goblin cold. Wally and Betty Yeti must find the ingredients to cure the Goblin's cold which Bobgoblin is suffering from, although not enough to affect his politeness, still referring to Betty as Miss Elizabeth Yeti.

episodes.name: Rock and Troll
episodes.overview: When Wally's father, Howard's favorite band cancels their concert because of a band member who's sick, Wally and his friends form a band to cheer him up.

episodes.name: Critter Campers
episodes.overview: Stan of the Swamp is running a "Critter Campers" scouting group. "Camper Doug" (Ogre) brings Borgelorp, "Camper Light Sprite" (Libby) brings Chickenphant, and "Camper Trollman" (Wally) brings Norville. "Camper Bobgoblin" shows up with his uncle Robgoblin's purple dragon, Hortis (whom he is borrowing for the day) and wants to be Wally's partner. Then Bobgoblin learns that He will have to be Great when he is Cooperating with Wally as a Partner.

episodes.name: The Big Cake Mistake
episodes.overview: Wally offers to fulfill his job at the bakery. It turns out the Cake Monster is gainfully employed there. When Cake Monster pours too much Power Flour in, the cakes got too big and caught the bakery on top of the cakes.

episodes.name: Dawn of the Zucchini
episodes.overview: Wally and Norville meet a gnome in the vegetable garden, who doesn't like his name "Zack" with the letter Z. Then Zack learns how great Z can be when Wally shows him the Magic Stick and can make words that Start with the Letter Z.

episodes.name: Ricky the Robot
episodes.overview: Gina's robot comes to life from Wally's magic word "Power". When Bobgoblin is Impatient and runs away with him, Wally and Gina set out to Retrieve him so Norville can have a turn.

episodes.name: A Flouse in the House
episodes.overview: Wally, Norville and Gina become detectives to discover who has been taking Gina's possessions from her house.

episodes.name: Young Norville
episodes.overview: When Norville got hit with the word "Young", Wally and Norville set out to find Ogre Doug so that he can create a Cure so Norville can return to Adulthood.

episodes.name: Snowgoblin
episodes.overview: Bobgoblin's snow goblin comes to life when Bobgoblin's magic pickle has been placed between the Eyes and the Mouth. Then Bobgoblin learns that Snowgoblins should live in the Mountains when he discovers that his house is Accidentally covered in Snow.

episodes.name: The Great Missing Potato
episodes.overview: Not to be confused with the earlier episode "The Great Wishing Potato". Bobgoblin looks after the wishing potato while Goblin Guard is away on his Day Off. When Bobgoblin accidentally loses the Potato, Wally and Norville help him Retrieve the Great Wishing Potato so that Squeaky Cyclops can fixed.

episodes.name: Going Coconuts
episodes.overview: Jeff warns Wally not to say the word coconut when watching his home and Bobgoblin overhears and tries to trick him into saying it. He fails but then says it himself, causing a bunch of coconuts to burst out of the closet and bounce around.

episodes.name: Buddy Pal Friend Day
episodes.overview: Everyone picks a pal and gives them a heartfelt gift on Buddy Pal Friend Day, but Bobgoblin receives a gift from Hattie and gives her nothing in return because Bobgoblin does not know how to Think about her, not about himself.

episodes.name: Keeping Cappie Happy
episodes.overview: Hattie's younger sister Cappie the Witch (previously shown in a photograph Hattie had in "The Explorer's Club") is introduced in person. Wally has to babysit her when her magical abilities awaken putting her older sister to sleep.

episodes.name: The Collar Caper
episodes.overview: During their game of "Green Sprite, Red Sprite" Norville's collar accidentally sinks into a lake, Libby Light Sprite comes up with a way to make their own submarine out of a bubble to retrieve it.

episodes.name: Wally's Great Big Birthday Hunt
episodes.overview: Wally's friends, dressed incognito, send him on a quest in which he must complete challenges and collect letters in order to discover the location of his birthday party.

episodes.name: Captain Animal
episodes.overview: Wally and Norville play superheroes (just like the early episode "Victor The Villain"). Ogre Doug dresses up a superhero named "Captain Animal" to play with them and finds where Borgelorp is but does not know how to be a superhero.

episodes.name: The Bathmobile
episodes.overview: Wally creates a bathmobile to help clean the town on Clean Up Day; a mud monster (Bobgoblin) roams the forest and gets everyone dirty.

episodes.name: Act Like Your Hat
episodes.overview: Wally makes his friends hats come to life for a hat party. Bobgoblin then stole Wally's hat and now they have to get his hat back.

episodes.name: The Chickephant's Getting Married
episodes.overview: Wally plans the Goorilla and Chickephant's wedding.

episodes.name: A Very Villainous Vacation
episodes.overview: Victor the Villain escapes from Wally's comic again and tries to ruin his family's beach vacation.

episodes.name: Ted the Bed
episodes.overview: Wally and his friends have a sleepover in the clubhouse, but when they forgot their sleeping bags, Wally must create a bed for them to sleep on.

episodes.name: Power Tie
episodes.overview: Bobgoblin gets a hold of Mr. Trollman's magic tie (given as a birthday gift from Mrs. Trollman). It's up to Wally to get it back before it goes out of hand.

episodes.name: Show and Tell and Run
episodes.overview: When Bobgoblin forgets to bring something for school show and tell, he uses the magic word "Wacky" from Wally's stick and accidentally causes wackiness all over town.

episodes.name: Sticky Picnic
episodes.overview: When Bobgoblin's drumstick gets broken, he asks Wally to repair it. However, when he tossed it, he and Wally get stuck. Now how are Wally and Bobgoblin going to go to Gina's party.

episodes.name: Cappie's Anormus Face
episodes.overview: Vikings Playing Music When Cappie Face Fells Better.

episodes.name: Best Friend
episodes.overview: Wally and norville are Best Friends
